  <description><![CDATA[<p>Situated at the forest's edge, Beausite Park Hotel is a family-run hotel offering traditional Swiss hospitality. Just a five-minute walk from the village centre, the elevated location allows for spectacular views of the Jungfrau and over <a data-udi="umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3}" title="Wengen">Wengen</a> village.</p>
<h2>A wellness area with mountain views</h2>
<p>The indoor swimming pool's floor-to-ceiling windows look out to the gardens and surrounding mountains, but if fresh water is more your thing then you can also take a dip in the garden's natural swimming pond.</p>
<p>Just want a moment to relax and soak it all in? There's a spa with two saunas, a steam room, a tepidarium, and a relaxation room.</p>
<h2>Culinary indulgence</h2>
<p>Breakfast is buffet-style, with hot eggs cooked to order and you won't go hungry in the evenings after a long day of activities: Dinner is a generous four-course feast and there's also comfortable lounge and bar.</p>]]></description>
