  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Spa &amp; wellness facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Indoor swimming pool and whirlpool with great views (children permitted under parental supervision)</li>
<li>Sauna area (adults only) with bio sauna (55°C), Finnish sauna (85 °C)</li>
<li>Steam room</li>
<li>Tepidarium (45°C )</li>
<li>Natural swimming pond</li>
<li>Small fitness room</li>
<li>Massage and beauty treatments (payable locally)</li>
<li>Pool towels</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Additional facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Large sun terrace</li>
<li>Gardens</li>
<li>Dog friendly</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Family facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cots and linen available (free up to two years old)</li>
<li>Baby listening service</li>
<li>Early meals available from 6.30pm - choose from adults or children's menu</li>
<li>Swimming pool open to children 7am-8pm (no lifeguard)</li>
<li>Spa area open to 16yrs+</li>
<li>Children's playroom (unsupervised) situated next to dining room (7am-10pm) with table football, games, and books</li>
<li>Giant chess board</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
